Replaces: gmp (<< 4.1.4-1), libmpfr-dev, libmpfr1, libmpfr1-64bit, libmpfr4, libmpfr4-64bit
Source: http://www.mpfr.org/mpfr-%v/mpfr-%v.tar.bz2
